  "tasbihatArba3Title": "TASBIḤĀT AL-ARBAʿA",
  "tasbihatArba3Subtitle": "Izingiswa ubunye kanye okwesine",
  "tasbihatArba3Info": "Ku-Shia jurisprudence, i-Tasbiḥāt al-Arbaʿa isikhathi i-Surah al-Fatiha (ubunye kanye okwesine) ye-Dhuhr, Asr, Maghrib, kanye ne-Isha. Kufanele ukuzikhumbula yonke indlela (wājib) futhi kumele isukela ngabathathu (mustaḥabb).",
  "tasbihatArba3Translation": "Zingisile uAllohu · Konke okukudumela kuAllohu\nAkekho onye kungcwele ngaphandle ku-Allohu · UAllohu unkulu kakhulu",
