  "tasbihatZahraSubtitle": "Ngemva kokukhuleka ngayinye · izimaddade ezingama-100",
  "tasbihatZahraOriginLabel": "Umsuka",
  "tasbihatZahraHadith": "U-Lady Fatima al-Zahra (sa) kwamusela uProfethe ﷺ umkhulu. Wathi: \"Kaloku ngakungikhombisa kucinzelo okungemele? Sikhumbula Subḥānallāh izinsuku ezingama-33, Alḥamdulillāh izinsuku ezingama-33, kanye noAllāhu Akbar izinsuku ezingama-34 ngemva kokukhuleka ngayinye. Lokho kungemele kakhulu kulomkhulu.\"",
  "tasbihatZahraHadithSource": "— Bihar al-Anwār, Vol. 85",
  "tasbihatZahraOpenCounter": "Vula Tasbīḥ Counter",
  "tasbihatDuasTitle": "IDUAS EZISIKISISWE",
  "tasbihatDuasSubtitle": "Emva kokugcina okukhuleka kwakho",
  "tasbihatDuaAyatKursiTitle": "Āyat al-Kursī",
  "tasbihatDuaAyatKursiWhen": "Ngemva kokukhuleka ngayinye okufanele",
  "tasbihatDuaAyatKursiSource": "Surah al-Baqarah 2:255",
  "tasbihatDuaAyatKursiNote": "Onaliphi umuntu ozingisa i-Āyat al-Kursī ngemva kokukhuleka ngayinye okufanele, akekho ekuseni ophakathi kwakhe nenkosi kungcwele ukufa. U-Imam al-Bāqir (a) wabe yiyo ina-verse enkulu ngazo zonke ku-Quran.",
  "tasbihatDuaSalawatTitle": "Ṣalawāt",
  "tasbihatDuaSalawatWhen": "Ngemva kokukhuleka ngayinye · i-seal konke izicelo",
  "tasbihatDuaSalawatSource": "Imam al-Ṣādiq (a) — Al-Kāfī",
  "tasbihatDuaSalawatNote": "Ukuthuma ilogo kuProfethe ﷺ kanye nemindeni yakhe enobugcinane (Āl Muḥammad) kumele kugcinwe idiche yediya ngayinye. U-Imam al-Ṣādiq (a) wabe: \"Onoma idiya ihintile de uthumele ilogo kuMuḥammad kanye nemindeni yakhe.\"",
  "tasbihatDuaFarajTitle": "Duʿā al-Faraj",
  "tasbihatDuaFarajWhen": "Ngemva kokukhuleka ngayinye · kukhomotsha lwe-Imam wezikhathi",
  "tasbihatDuaFarajSource": "Oqondiswe ngu-Imam al-Ḥasan al-ʿAskarī (a)",
  "tasbihatDuaFarajNote": "Idua yokubuya kwe-Imam al-Mahdī (af), u-Imam oweshumi nalambili, oqondiswe nguBaba wakhe. Izingiswa yensuku nje abalifuthe be-Shia emva kokukhuleka ngayinye njengomsebenzi wokukholo ku-Imam ophilayo.",
  "tasbihatDuaTasbihFatimaTitle": "Tasbīḥ weNtombazane Fāṭima",
  "tasbihatDuaTasbihFatimaWhen": "Ngemva kwe-Maghrib & Isha · ikhusulwa ngengeziwe",
  "tasbihatDuaTasbihFatimaSource": "Imam al-Bāqir (a) — Biḥār al-Anwār",
  "tasbihatDuaTasbihFatimaNote": "U-Imam al-Bāqir (a) wabe ukuba uzingisa i-Tasbīḥ al-Zahrā ngemva kwe-Isha ngaphambi kokuphinga kununga ngaphandle kwamarakʿah angama-1000. Okukhazimula kwayo kukhwele emadodeni.",
